vatar/7bb495a607f1f7e4a231404a42b81936?s=30\" alt=\"Benoit Catherineau\" /></a> <a class=\"web\" href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ben-kenobi\">Benoît Catherineau</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"wp-credits-list\">&#8230; ainsi que<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ado666\"> ado666</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dakotapearl\">dakotapearl</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fge0\">Franck Gervais</a> et <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jaddle\">jaddle</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-credits-list\">C&rsquo;est grâce à eux que la version française est disponible en quasi simultanéité que la version originale. Merci à eux !</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 class=\"wp-credits-list\">Ils en parlent aussi&#8230;</h2>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"wp-credits-list\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2014/12/dinah/\">WordPress.org</a> (dont est tiré l&rsquo;article ci-dessus)</li>\n<li class=\"wp-credits-list\"><a href=\"http://wptavern.com/wordpress-4-1-dinah-released\">WP Tavern</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=wwuVe9q-5x0:h27tNRVwt-U:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=wwuVe9q-5x0:h27tNRVwt-U:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=wwuVe9q-5x0:h27tNRVwt-U:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=wwuVe9q-5x0:h27tNRVwt-U:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=wwuVe9q-5x0:h27tNRVwt-U:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=wwuVe9q-5x0:h27tNRVwt-U:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"//feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/wwuVe9q-5x0\" height=